Hey guys when trying to download the latest wpilib version for windows from the wpilib website we are getting this error:

Error 1101 Ray ID: 9240ec53aecac97b • 2025-03-21 22:35:34 UTC

Worker threw exception

What happened?

You’ve requested a page on a website (packages.wpilib.workers.dev) that is on the Cloudflare network. An unknown error occurred while rendering the page.

What can I do?

If you are the owner of this website:
you should login to Cloudflare and check the error logs for packages.wpilib.workers.dev.

Cloudflare Ray ID: 9240ec53aecac97b •

We have our competition tomorrow and are stressing out. The error is appearing on everyone laptops and previous versions
